&lt;li&gt;Design and implement scalable, maintainable, and high-performance user interfaces using modern frontend technologies like React and TypeScript.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with backend engineers, designers, product managers, and senior leadership to turn product and technical visions into tangible roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain low-latency, highly reliable frontend surfaces to deliver a world-class user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write high-quality, well-tested code to meet the needs of Coinbase’s growing user base.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
