&lt;li&gt;You’re excited to build new tools and systems that simplify workflows, eliminate toil, and increase development velocity across the company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
