&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a monorepo and building developer tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with MergeQueue systems, remote build execution, or caching strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to Docker, Kubernetes, Cloud infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with artifact management (e.g., Artifactory)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
