&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82z5hz72z4erz72zz90z8z89z44dz122zjz69zdz76zaz77zuz80z2z84zvz76zgxz74zs&quot;&gt;Collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams, including product managers, designers, and other engineers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82z5hz72z4erz72zz90z8z89z44dz122zjz69zdz76zaz77zuz80z2z84zvz76zgxz74zs&quot;&gt;Participate in the process of continuous deployment, including code reviews and deploys.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82z5hz72z4erz72zz90z8z89z44dz122zjz69zdz76zaz77zuz80z2z84zvz76zgxz74zs&quot;&gt;Participate in on-call rotations, which entails being available for calls during both core and non-core business hours.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82z5hz72z4erz72zz90z8z89z44dz122zjz69zdz76zaz77zuz80z2z84zvz76zgxz74zs&quot;&gt;Debug customer issues using logs, metrics, and traces.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
